1021
01:00:50,640 --> 01:00:51,810
Cảm ơn.

1022
01:00:52,810 --> 01:00:53,810
Anh đưa tôi đi đâu vậy?

1023
01:00:54,110 --> 01:00:55,470
Tôi muốn cho anh xem 1 thứ.

1024
01:00:55,490 --> 01:00:56,490
